---
const pageTitle = "About Me";
const name = "Delilah";
const job = "Life Insurance Agent, Student, and Builder";
const hobbies = ["building my future", "learning new things (even when it’s hard)", "helping and encouraging others", "creating things — websites, ideas, goals", "growing through challenges", "spending time with my kids",];
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>

    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

      html, body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: #f8f5f2;
        color: #1f1a17;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 60px 24px;
      }

      h1, h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        color: #2c1d18;
        line-height: 1.15;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      p, li, a {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      a {
        color: #7a2e2e;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .nav {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .nav a {
        margin-right: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .hero-tag {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #ead9cf;
        color: #5d2a2a;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: #5a4a42;
        max-width: 680px;
      }

      .card {
        background: #fffdfb;
        border: 1px solid #eadfd7;
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(44, 29, 24, 0.06);
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about/">About</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
      </nav>

      <span class="hero-tag">About</span>
      <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>

      <p class="subtitle">
       <p class="subtitle">
I’ve gone through my share of trials, setbacks, and challenges — learning as I go and trying to become a better version of myself.
I’m someone who reflects, grows, and keeps pushing forward, especially for my kids and the future I’m building for them.

This is who I’ve always been, long before life insurance — someone who keeps going, even when things feel uncertain.

I don’t have it all figured out… but I don’t quit either.
</p>
      </p>

  <section class="card">
  <h2>A little about me</h2>
  <p>
    I’ve always stayed resilient through life’s testing waters.
  </p>

  <div class="values">
  <p>✨ Trusting the process, walking blindly in faith</p>
  <p>✨ Choosing growth, even when it’s uncomfortable</p>
  <p>✨ Showing up, even when I feel unsure</p>
  <p>✨ Building a better future for my kids</p>
  <p>✨ Turning what I’ve been through into strength</p>

</div>
  
</section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>